name: chart-my-marathon
description: ## Summary I’ve been an enthusiastic (if slow) runner since I was in high school. If there’s one thing we runners love, its our data. I have the privledge of being chosen for the New York City Marathon's 2016 lottery last year, so my husband and I took a trip to NYC last November. Going to NYC was a blast, and I finished the race 4:31 - that is, 4 hours and 31 minutes. A PR for me!
